        "setup": "Go to the [Entrust Dashboard](https://dashboard.onfido.com/), open **Developers** → **API authentication** → **Tokens**, then click **Generate API token** and choose **Sandbox** or **Live**. Sandbox tokens start with `api_sandbox`; live tokens start with `api_live`. Use tokens only server-side.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
      "onfido_oauth_app": {
        "type": "oauth2_cc",
        "label": "OAuth application / client credentials",
        "generateUrl": "https://dashboard.onfido.com/",
        "setup": "Go to the [Entrust Dashboard](https://dashboard.onfido.com/), open **Developers** → **API authentication** → **OAuth applications**, then click **Create application**. Pick sandbox or live, select scopes, save, and copy the `client_id` and `client_secret`. Use them to mint a short-lived OAuth access token with the API's client-credentials flow. OAuth access tokens are available for API v3.6 onwards.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      }
    },
